  <entry>
    <title>Shell编程入门</title>
    <link href="http://example.com/2021/12/18/Shell%E7%BC%96%E7%A8%8B/"/>
    <id>http://example.com/2021/12/18/Shell%E7%BC%96%E7%A8%8B/</id>
    <published>2021-12-17T23:00:38.000Z</published>
    <updated>2021-12-18T16:04:05.769Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>引用内容的符号：</p><blockquote><p>单引号：所见即所得</p><p>双引号：解析变量（把所输入内容看做整体）</p><p>反引号：解析命令</p><p>无引号：与双引号类似</p></blockquote><ul><li><h5 id="为什么学习Shell编程"><a href="#为什么学习Shell编程" class="headerlink" title="为什么学习Shell编程"></a>为什么学习Shell编程</h5><p>Linux系统中会大量的使用Shell，工作中我们也需要自动化实现业务，<br>例如：自动备份、监控、自动安装服务。</p><p>Shell编程是Linux运维人员必须要会的编程语言。最简单的编程语言。<br>编程也是运维人员必须具备的本领：<br>Shell、Python是运维人员必须具备的本领</p></li><li><h5 id="什么是Shell"><a href="#什么是Shell" class="headerlink" title="什么是Shell"></a>什么是Shell</h5><p>Shell就是一个命令解释器（翻译官），命令行的命令以及脚本都会通过shell解释，传给操作系统，处理后在输出给用户</p></li><li><h5 id="什么是Shell脚本"><a href="#什么是Shell脚本" class="headerlink" title="什么是Shell脚本"></a>什么是Shell脚本</h5><p>程序、命令放入文件里执行，这个文件和脚本称为Shell脚本文件</p></li><li><h5 id="Shell变量"><a href="#Shell变量" class="headerlink" title="Shell变量"></a>Shell变量</h5><ol><li><p>全局变量（环境变量）</p><p>在整个系统中生效，一般为大写字母。系统中默认就存在一些这样的变量，满足系统和程序的需求。</p><p>系统默认环境变量示例：</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">[root@centos ~]#echo $PS1</span><br><span class="line">[\[\e[34;1m\]\u@\[\e[0m\]\[\e[32;1m\]\H\[\e[0m\]\[\e[31;1m\] \w\[\e[0m\]]\$</span><br><span class="line">[root@centos ~]#echo $PATH </span><br><span class="line">/usr/local/sbin:/usr/local/bin:/usr/sbin:/usr/bin:/root/bin</span><br><span class="line">[root@centos ~]#echo $HOME</span><br><span class="line">/root</span><br><span class="line">[root@centos ~]#echo $SHELL</span><br><span class="line">/bin/bash</span><br><span class="line">[root@centos ~]#echo $PWD</span><br><span class="line">/root</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>自定义环境变量：</p><p>方法1：</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">[root@centos ~]#export JACK=&quot;I am Jack&quot;</span><br><span class="line">[root@centos ~]#echo $JACK</span><br><span class="line">I am Jack</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>方法2：</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">[root@centos ~]#ANDY=&quot;I am Andy&quot;</span><br><span class="line">[root@centos ~]#echo $ANDY</span><br><span class="line">I am Andy</span><br><span class="line">[root@centos ~]#echo $&#123;ANDY&#125;   #可以用&#123;&#125;，多个变量时用以区分</span><br><span class="line">I am Andy</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>CenOS环境变量优先级配置文件</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">/etc/profile</span><br><span class="line">~/.bash_profile</span><br><span class="line">~/.bashrc</span><br><span class="line">/etc/bashrc    #推荐以后把环境变量放入/etc/bashrc内，优先级最大</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p>局部变量（普通变量）</p><p>局部变量是编写Shell脚本最常用的变量</p><p>表示方式：</p><p>​                 变量名=值    </p><p>​                        a=1</p><p>命名规则：</p><p>​                 字母、下划线、数字、==不能以数字开头==</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">=赋值符 </span><br><span class="line">值 变量内容</span><br><span class="line">（引用内容的符号：单引号、双引号、反引号、不加引号）</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>==注意：赋值符号两边不能有空格==</p></li></ol></li><li><h5 id="表达式"><a href="#表达式" class="headerlink" title="表达式"></a>表达式</h5><ol><li><p>[  ] 中括号表达式</p><p>==中括号里面内容两端必须要有空格==</p><p>==字符串要加双引号==</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">[root@centos ~]#[ &quot;a&quot; = &quot;b&quot; ] &amp;&amp; echo 1 || echo 0</span><br><span class="line">0</span><br><span class="line">[root@centos ~]#[ &quot;a&quot; = &quot;a&quot; ] &amp;&amp; echo 1 || echo 0</span><br><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">如果表达式成立，打印1，否则打印0</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p>整数表达式</p><p>==1)整数表达式符 两端必须要有空格<br>2)中括号里面两端必须要有空格。<br>3)变量和比较的内容，不需要加引号。==</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&gt;      -gtgreater than 大于</span><br><span class="line">&gt;=     -gegreater equal 大等于</span><br><span class="line">&lt;      -ltless than    小于</span><br><span class="line">&lt;=     -le    less equal   小等于</span><br><span class="line">=      -eq     equal       等于</span><br><span class="line">≠      -ne    not equal    不等于</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">[root@centos ~]#a=1</span><br><span class="line">[root@centos ~]#[ $a -eq 2 ] &amp;&amp; echo 1 || echo 0</span><br><span class="line">0</span><br><span class="line">[root@centos ~]#[ $a -eq 1 ] &amp;&amp; echo 1 || echo 0</span><br><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">如果表达式成立，打印1，否则打印0</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p>字符串表达式</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">-n 变量内容长度【不】为0时，为真(表达式正确)not zero</span><br><span class="line">-z 变量内容长度为0时，为真(表达式正确)         zero</span><br><span class="line">a == a 字符串是否相同```</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>==说明：字符串要加双引号==</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">[root@centos ~]#jack=&quot;I am Jack&quot;</span><br><span class="line">[root@centos ~]#echo $jack</span><br><span class="line">I am Jack</span><br><span class="line">[root@centos ~]#[ -z &quot;$jack&quot; ] &amp;&amp; echo 1 || echo 0</span><br><span class="line">0</span><br><span class="line">[root@centos ~]#[ -n &quot;$jack&quot; ] &amp;&amp; echo 1 || echo 0</span><br><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">为jack赋值，然后查看变量长度是否为0，是打印0，否则打印1</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li></ol></li><li><h5 id="Shell判断句"><a href="#Shell判断句" class="headerlink" title="Shell判断句"></a>Shell判断句</h5><p>if 判断句语法     </p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">if [ 表达式 ]</span><br><span class="line">then</span><br><span class="line">   命令</span><br><span class="line">fi</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">[root@centos ~]#cat test.sh </span><br><span class="line">#!/bin/bash</span><br><span class="line">a=10</span><br><span class="line">if [ $a -gt 1 ]</span><br><span class="line">then</span><br><span class="line">    echo 1</span><br><span class="line">fi</span><br><span class="line">[root@centos ~]#bash test.sh </span><br><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">#如果变量a大于1，打印1</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>如果……否则示例：</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">[root@centos ~]#cat test.sh </span><br><span class="line">#!/bin/bash</span><br><span class="line">a=10</span><br><span class="line">if [ $a -gt 1 ]</span><br><span class="line">then</span><br><span class="line">    echo 1</span><br><span class="line">else </span><br><span class="line">    echo 0</span><br><span class="line">fi</span><br><span class="line">[root@centos ~]#bash test.sh </span><br><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">#如果变量a大于1，打印1，否则打印0</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>趣味尝试：</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">[root@centos ~]#cat test.sh </span><br><span class="line">#!/bin/bash</span><br><span class="line">boy=&quot;潜力股&quot;</span><br><span class="line">if [ &quot;$boy&quot; ==  &quot;潜力股&quot; ]</span><br><span class="line">then</span><br><span class="line">    echo &quot;先和你谈谈朋友&quot;</span><br><span class="line">else</span><br><span class="line">    echo &quot;白白&quot;</span><br><span class="line">fi</span><br><span class="line">[root@centos ~]#bash test.sh </span><br><span class="line">先和你谈谈朋友</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">[root@centos ~]#cat test.sh </span><br><span class="line">if [ $(date +%w) -eq 6 ]</span><br><span class="line">then </span><br><span class="line">    echo &quot;一起去旅游吧&quot;</span><br><span class="line">else</span><br><span class="line">    echo &quot;还是好好上课吧&quot;</span><br><span class="line">fi</span><br><span class="line">[root@centos ~]#bash test.sh </span><br><span class="line">还是好好上课吧</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>==实现多条件==</p><p>方法1：</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">[root@centos ~]#cat test.sh </span><br><span class="line">if [ $(date +%w) -eq 6 ] || [ $(date +%w) -eq 0 ]</span><br><span class="line">then </span><br><span class="line">    echo &quot;一起去旅游吧&quot;</span><br><span class="line">else</span><br><span class="line">    echo &quot;还是好好上课吧&quot;</span><br><span class="line">fi</span><br><span class="line">[root@centos ~]#bash test.sh </span><br><span class="line">还是好好上课吧</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>方法2：</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">read命令 交互式读取用户输入</span><br><span class="line">-p &quot;提醒：&quot;</span><br><span class="line">-t &quot;多长时间内等待输入&quot;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br><span class="line">26</span><br><span class="line">27</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">[root@centos ~/shsh]#cat test.sh </span><br><span class="line">#!/bin/bash</span><br><span class="line">read -p &quot;请输入指令：&quot; ps</span><br><span class="line">if [ &quot;$ps&quot; == &quot;123&quot; ]</span><br><span class="line">then</span><br><span class="line">    echo &quot;指令正确,启动飞船&quot;</span><br><span class="line">elif [ &quot;$ps&quot; == &quot;456&quot; ]</span><br><span class="line">then</span><br><span class="line">    echo &quot;特殊指令,前往地球&quot;</span><br><span class="line">elif [ &quot;$ps&quot; == &quot;789&quot; ]</span><br><span class="line">then </span><br><span class="line">    echo &quot;超级指令，回家&quot;</span><br><span class="line">else</span><br><span class="line">    echo &quot;指令错误,启动自毁&quot;   </span><br><span class="line">fi</span><br><span class="line">[root@centos ~/shsh]#bash test.sh </span><br><span class="line">请输入指令：123</span><br><span class="line">指令正确,启动飞船</span><br><span class="line">[root@centos ~/shsh]#bash test.sh </span><br><span class="line">请输入指令：456</span><br><span class="line">特殊指令,前往地球</span><br><span class="line">[root@centos ~/shsh]#bash test.sh </span><br><span class="line">请输入指令：789</span><br><span class="line">超级指令，回家</span><br><span class="line">[root@centos ~/shsh]#bash test.sh </span><br><span class="line">请输入指令：000</span><br><span class="line">指令错误,启动自毁</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><h5 id="练习题：Shell编程实现-两个整数比较大小"><a href="#练习题：Shell编程实现-两个整数比较大小" class="headerlink" title="练习题：Shell编程实现 两个整数比较大小"></a>练习题：Shell编程实现 两个整数比较大小</h5><p>方法1：</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">[root@centos ~]#bash daxiao.sh </span><br><span class="line">请输入两个数字：11 22</span><br><span class="line">11&lt;22</span><br><span class="line">[root@centos ~]#bash daxiao.sh </span><br><span class="line">请输入两个数字：22 11</span><br><span class="line">22&gt;11</span><br><span class="line">[root@centos ~]#bash daxiao.sh </span><br><span class="line">请输入两个数字：11 11</span><br><span class="line">11=11</span><br><span class="line">[root@centos ~]#cat daxiao.sh </span><br><span class="line">#!/bin/bash</span><br><span class="line">read -p &quot;请输入两个数字：&quot; a b</span><br><span class="line">if [ $a -gt $b ] </span><br><span class="line">then</span><br><span class="line">    echo &quot;$a&gt;$b&quot;</span><br><span class="line">elif [ $a -eq $b ] </span><br><span class="line">then </span><br><span class="line">    echo &quot;$a=$b&quot;</span><br><span class="line">else </span><br><span class="line">    echo &quot;$a&lt;$b&quot;</span><br><span class="line">fi</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>方法2：</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">特殊位置变量：</span><br><span class="line">$1 脚本文件的第一个参数赋值给$1</span><br><span class="line">$2 脚本文件的第二个参数赋值给$2</span><br><span class="line">[root@centos ~]#cat b.sh</span><br><span class="line">echo $1 $2</span><br><span class="line">[root@centos ~]#bash b.sh b1 b2</span><br><span class="line">b1 b2#b1就是$1的输出结果   b2就是$2的输出结果</span><br><span class="line">#为$1赋值b1   为$2赋值b2（）</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">[root@centos ~]#cat daxiao.sh </span><br><span class="line">#!/bin/bash</span><br><span class="line">a=$1</span><br><span class="line">b=$2</span><br><span class="line">if [ $a -gt $b ] </span><br><span class="line">then</span><br><span class="line">    echo &quot;$a&gt;$b&quot;</span><br><span class="line">elif [ $a -eq $b ] </span><br><span class="line">then </span><br><span class="line">    echo &quot;$a=$b&quot;</span><br><span class="line">else </span><br><span class="line">    echo &quot;$a&lt;$b&quot;</span><br><span class="line">fi</span><br><span class="line">[root@centos ~]#bash daxiao.sh 11 22</span><br><span class="line">11&lt;22</span><br><span class="line">[root@centos ~]#bash daxiao.sh 22 11</span><br><span class="line">22&gt;11</span><br><span class="line">[root@centos ~]#bash daxiao.sh 22 22</span><br><span class="line">22=22</span><br><span class="line">脚本后直接输入数字，取值比较</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><h5 id="for循环"><a href="#for循环" class="headerlink" title="for循环"></a>for循环</h5><p>语法：</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">for n in 取值列表</span><br><span class="line">do</span><br><span class="line">    执行命令</span><br><span class="line">done</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>示例：</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br><span class="line">26</span><br><span class="line">27</span><br><span class="line">28</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">[root@centos ~]#cat for.sh </span><br><span class="line">#!/bin/bash</span><br><span class="line">for n in 1 2 3 4 5</span><br><span class="line">do </span><br><span class="line">    echo &quot;$n&quot;</span><br><span class="line">done</span><br><span class="line">[root@centos ~]#bash for.sh </span><br><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">[root@centos ~]#bash -x for.sh   # -x 查看执行过程</span><br><span class="line">+ for n in 1 2 3 4 5</span><br><span class="line">+ echo 1</span><br><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">+ for n in 1 2 3 4 5</span><br><span class="line">+ echo 2</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">+ for n in 1 2 3 4 5</span><br><span class="line">+ echo 3</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">+ for n in 1 2 3 4 5</span><br><span class="line">+ echo 4</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">+ for n in 1 2 3 4 5</span><br><span class="line">+ echo 5</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>==bash -x 查看执行过程==</p><p>序列for循环</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br><span class="line">26</span><br><span class="line">27</span><br><span class="line">28</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">[root@centos ~]#cat for.sh </span><br><span class="line">#!/bin/bash</span><br><span class="line">for n in &#123;1..5&#125;</span><br><span class="line">do </span><br><span class="line">    echo &quot;$n&quot;</span><br><span class="line">done</span><br><span class="line">[root@centos ~]#bash -x for.sh </span><br><span class="line">+ for n in &#x27;&#123;1..5&#125;&#x27;</span><br><span class="line">+ echo 1</span><br><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">+ for n in &#x27;&#123;1..5&#125;&#x27;</span><br><span class="line">+ echo 2</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">+ for n in &#x27;&#123;1..5&#125;&#x27;</span><br><span class="line">+ echo 3</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">+ for n in &#x27;&#123;1..5&#125;&#x27;</span><br><span class="line">+ echo 4</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">+ for n in &#x27;&#123;1..5&#125;&#x27;</span><br><span class="line">+ echo 5</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">[root@centos ~]#bash for.sh </span><br><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>进阶：打印254个IP地址192.168.0.1—192.168.0.254</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">[root@centos ~]#cat forip.sh </span><br><span class="line">#!/bin/bash</span><br><span class="line">for n in &#123;1..254&#125;</span><br><span class="line">do </span><br><span class="line">    echo &quot;192.168.0.$n&quot;</span><br><span class="line">done</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">[root@centos ~]#cat forip.sh </span><br><span class="line">#!/bin/bash</span><br><span class="line">for n in 192.168.0.&#123;1..254&#125;</span><br><span class="line">do </span><br><span class="line">    echo $n</span><br><span class="line">done</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><h5 id="书写脚本习惯："><a href="#书写脚本习惯：" class="headerlink" title="书写脚本习惯："></a>书写脚本习惯：</h5><p>1.以.sh结尾。<br>2.脚本开头第一行 #!/bin/bash 脚本内容由谁解释。</p><p>  由于Linux下默认是bash，所以也可以不写这一行。</p></li><li><h5 id="课后练习"><a href="#课后练习" class="headerlink" title="课后练习"></a>课后练习</h5><p>1、比较整数大小。</p><p>2、判断日期，每周六日去旅游，其它时间上课</p><p>3、取出当前系统Ip地址，判断是否为192.168.0.111，如果是提示正确，如果不是给出提示</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">[root@centos ~/shsh]#cat ip.sh </span><br><span class="line">#!/bin/bash</span><br><span class="line">ipadd=$(ifconfig eth0 | sed -nr &#x27;s#^.*inet (.*)net.*$#\1#gp&#x27;) </span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">if [ $ipadd == &quot;192.168.0.111&quot; ]</span><br><span class="line">then</span><br><span class="line">    echo &quot;系统IP为192.168.0.111验证通过&quot;</span><br><span class="line">else</span><br><span class="line">    echo &quot;系统IP验证失败，当前IP地址：$ipadd&quot;</span><br><span class="line">fi</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>4、打印192.168.0.100–192.168.0.120个Ip地址，当IP地址为系统IP地址时，给出某IP是系统IP的提示</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">#!/bin/bash</span><br><span class="line">for n in 192.168.0.&#123;100..120&#125;</span><br><span class="line">do</span><br><span class="line">echo &quot;$n&quot;</span><br><span class="line">if [ $n == &quot;192.168.0.111&quot; ]</span><br><span class="line">then </span><br><span class="line">    echo &quot;******$n 匹配成功，此IP为系统IP地址******&quot;</span><br><span class="line">else</span><br><span class="line">    echo &quot;匹配失败&quot;</span><br><span class="line">fi</span><br><span class="line">done </span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li></ul><p>​     </p>]]></content>
    
    
      
      
